Use Ruby-on-Rails framework to build an online bookstore website.

The website have these functionalities:

 

 

1. List all books (with book cover images), show individual book info

2. search books.

3. add/edit/delete books.

4. login page to be able to do the #3 function

5. add to shopping cart, show shopping card for list of items selected.

6. check out the selected items.
